#################################################################################################

Program Description:

ShortcutFactory is an application for automatically generating shortcuts (.lnk files) through batch processing.

Features:

- Select a sample file to determine the file type to search for.

- Select the source directory in which to search (recursively) for files of this type.

- Select the target directory in which the shortcuts to the files of the specified type found in the source directory will be stored.

- Start the process by clicking the "Generate" button.

- Files with identical file names will be overwritten.

Enjoy!

